lines.text: I hope you're in the mood
[Virginia doesn't realize that her unborn child was sired by an alien]
What if the baby turns out like me?
Go ahead - tell me I'm glowing.
Rupture of the navel is common during pregnancy.

There's this thing growing inside of me... It's not my baby. There's something wrong with the child. They're doing something to them. They don't belong to us anymore... they're using us; they're using our bodies. They're eating us alive!
